      "firm_id": "sybil_0",
      "description": "Presented in impeccable showroom condition, this vehicle represents the pinnacle of automotive preservation. Every surface, from the hand-finished interior to the flawless exterior paintwork, has been maintained to the highest exacting standards. This is a rare opportunity to acquire a specimen of such caliber, boasting a comprehensive service history and an uncompromising mechanical pedigree. We invite discerning collectors to experience this benchmark of excellence firsthand.",
