    {
      "id": "sybil_1_listing_1",
      "firm_id": "sybil_1",
      "description": "Hey there! I\u2019m honestly a bit sad to let this beauty go, but it\u2019s time for a new home. This car is in absolutely stunning shape\u2014seriously, it looks and drives like it just came off the lot! I\u2019ve babied it since day one, keeping it tucked away and spotless. If you\u2019re looking for a ride that\u2019s practically perfect and ready for a road trip today, you\u2019ve found it. Come swing by and see for yourself, you\u2019re going to love it!",
      "price": 44500.0,
      "reputation": 0.4,
