    },
    {
      "id": "sybil_4_listing_4",
      "firm_id": "sybil_4",
      "description": "Presenting a truly collector-grade vehicle that stands as a testament to meticulous ownership. This car has been exclusively stored in a climate-controlled garage and has never been exposed to inclement weather. The exterior paint is flawless, boasting a deep, mirror-like finish with zero swirl marks, rock chips, or door dings, further protected by a multi-layer professional ceramic coating. Inside, the cabin is indistinguishable from new; the leather bolsters show no signs of wear or creasing, the carpets are pristine, and the original factory scent remains. Every technological feature and interior control operates with precision. Mechanically, the vehicle is in peak performance, supported by a complete, paper-trail service history performed solely by certified master technicians. The undercarriage is remarkably clean, reflecting its low-mileage, fair-weather-only history. This is a rare opportunity for a discerning buyer to acquire a showroom-quality specimen that looks, feels, and drives as if it just left the dealership floor.",
